{"id":"api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor","title":"CheckboxControlValueAccessor","contents":"\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor\", \"name\": \"CheckboxControlValueAccessor\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/forms/src/directives/checkbox_value_accessor.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L18-L66\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/directives/checkbox_value_accessor.ts#L18-L66\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"checkboxcontrolvalueaccessor\">CheckboxControlValueAccessor<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor#checkboxcontrolvalueaccessor\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">一個 <code><a href=\"api/forms/ControlValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ControlValueAccessor</a></code>，用於寫入值並監聽複選框輸入元素上的更改。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A <code><a href=\"api/forms/ControlValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ControlValueAccessor</a></code> for writing a value and listening to changes on a checkbox input\nelement.</p>\n\n\n    \n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  \n\n  \n\n<h2 id=\"exported-from\">Exported from<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor#exported-from\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n\n  <li>\n    \n    <a href=\"api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">ReactiveFormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n    \n  </li>\n\n  <li>\n    \n    <a href=\"api/forms/FormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">FormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n    \n  </li>\n\n</ul>\n\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">選擇器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <ul>\n    <li><code>input[type=checkbox][<a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formControlName</a>]</code></li>\n    \n    <li><code>input[type=checkbox][formControl]</code></li>\n    \n    <li><code>input[type=checkbox][<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]</code></li>\n    \n  </ul>\n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n    <h3 id=\"using-a-checkbox-with-a-reactive-form\" translation-result=\"on\">使用帶有響應式表單的複選框。<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor#using-a-checkbox-with-a-reactive-form\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"using-a-checkbox-with-a-reactive-form\">Using a checkbox with a reactive form.<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor#using-a-checkbox-with-a-reactive-form\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">以下範例顯示瞭如何將複選框與響應式表單一起使用。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example shows how to use a checkbox with a reactive form.</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nconst rememberLoginControl = new <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>();\n</code-example>\n<code-example>\n&lt;input type=\"checkbox\" [formControl]=\"rememberLoginControl\"&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/ControlValueAccessor\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor#checkboxcontrolvalueaccessor\n - api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor#description\n - api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor#exported-from\n - api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor#selectors\n - api/forms/CheckboxControlValueAccessor#using-a-checkbox-with-a-reactive-form\n - api/forms/ControlValueAccessor\n - api/forms/FormControl\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/forms/src/directives/checkbox_value_accessor.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L18-L66\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/directives/checkbox_value_accessor.ts#L18-L66\n-->"}